3035	// (rbgjl01-ensconce-capture.sh). The guard cannot fire under natural minting:
3036	// each ensconce mints a fresh second-grained stamp, so two CLI captures land on
3037	// distinct touchmarks. We pin the stamp via the buo tweak channel
3038	// (RBTDRC_ENSCONCE_STAMP_TWEAK_NAME) to drive both captures onto ONE touchmark.
